features: Ultimate Set To Stay Neatly Organized: Now, that's what you call a fine selection! ZICOTOs’ huge modern sticky notes set offers 528 sheets in total ensuring there are always matching note taking supplies at hand for the office, college school or bible study use

Super Cute Pastel Colors: You’re sure to love the range of beautiful pastel colors the sticky notes come with - organizing & staying on track has never been prettier! As harmonic office & back to school supplies, they are perfect to color code notes, tasks & co.

Extra Practical - Great Variation In Sizes: Whether stuck on paper, books, walls, your computer or other surfaces, you have full choice of differently sized sticky notes, all the way up to large sheets offering ample space to put your ideas & thoughts down on paper

Endless Possibilities - Perfect Versatile Use: The sticky notes come in extremely useful in a multitude of applications, e. g. you can use them conveniently as teacher supplies or school supplies for college students to annotate books and as cute office supplies for women & men

All In One Place & Easy At Hand: Thanks to the sturdy, long-lasting hardcover case, you can carry the sticky notes with ease, always having them with you in case an exciting thought pops up at any time - a clever, forward-thinking and brilliant design
body.description: Cute Sticky Notes Set by ZICOTO: Your persuasive and attention-grabbing all-round talent Getting ideas and thoughts out of your head and onto paper - thanks to the modern sticky notes set you can do it the smart and pretty way! ZICOTOs’ set with a total of 528 sheets in a clever variety of sizes is here for you to capture any new ideas and information quickly, ultimately enhancing your productivity, reading as well as learning skills. Get things done the most effective way whether you’re at the office, school or home, by staying organized neatly. The sticky notes come in beautiful pastel colors - they’re not only pleasing to the eye but also perfect to work with, e. g. in terms of color coding ideas, project responsibilities, tasks, highlighting book sections, etc.! Super versatile use: In addition to the cute color options, the great variation of sizes makes the sticky notes even more of an unparalleled planning and organizing tool. From smaller sticky notes that work great as bible study supplies and for bookmarking to large sheets offering ample space for notes, lists, to do’s and more - the ultimate set has it all included! Whether used teacher supplies, college or school supplies, at home or in the office, the sticky notes are made for everyday use. They are organized in a sturdy durable hardcover case, making it super easy for you to carry them with you - all in one place.
